{"MALMA":[{"def":"A spotted trout (Salvelinus malma), inhabiting Northern America, west of the Rocky Mountains; -- called also Dolly Varden trout, bull trout, red-spotted trout, and golet.","pos":""}],"MALMAG":[{"def":"The tarsius, or spectral lemur.","pos":""}],"MALMSEY":[{"def":"A kind of sweet wine from Crete, the Canary Islands, etc.","pos":""}]}